title: Various Artists [2006] i fear for us
description:
D.i.Y  Do it Yer FUCKIN&#039; self

	it starts small, as small as sweing on a patch, or posting flyers for a local 
	show, and then it grows. you decide to say "fuck the bus, and fuck cars" and get 
	a bike and you can get around town for free, and usually faster than by vehicle. 
	you realize that you can put on your own shows, and promote them yourself. you 
	can copy and distribute a zine or a pamphlet and hand it out yourself, and find 
	radical bookstores and other places that will carry them. you can use spray paint 
	and canvas to make your own patches, and you will meet people who live this way, 
	and you can combine your efforts. we made this compilation that way. what&#039;ll you 
	make?

	...onwards,downwards...
